              : "üéß Listening..."}
          </p>
          <p>Violations: {violations}/3</p>
        </div>
      )}

      {examTerminated && (
        <div>
          <h3>‚úñ Exam Terminated</h3>
          <p>Too many violations detected. Please contact your instructor.</p>
        </div>
      )}
    </div>
  );
};

